These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, salsa, rock, indie
1. the fan of salsa is between the fan of rock and the fan of indie##2
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | house | indie | salsa | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, almond-milk, fanta
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking water and the person drinking soy-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | water | fanta | soy-milk | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, rabbit, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
3. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | hamster | guinea-pig | rabbit | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, orange, eggplant, corn
1. the person eating eggplant is between the person eating orange and the person eating cabbage##2
