3. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby   | collecting | skydiving | singing | reading |

