2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | fanta | tea | sprite |

 